\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 An eternal perspective from Jesus. What is real. Jesus said my kingdom is not of this world. Train your mind to distinguish between a temporal fact and an eternal reality. }
\par\plain \f0\fs22\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 I search for truth }
\par\plain \f0\fs22\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 The course and Urantia book give us some pretty exciting possibilities if we want to push our mental training beyond current norms. The Course says forgiveness is the key to accessing the higher mind functions. The UB gives us plenty of information to help us understand what can happen should we push deeper into the superconscious. It gives us warnings and encouragement. Transcending our current conscious state was much further out of reach before these two books were available. Now we have an instruction book to show us the way. Pursue a path few have had the opportunity to pursue. }
