\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 Another example of unconscious healing by Jesus. (152:0.3) When Jesus heard this, he took the woman by the hand and, lifting her up, said: "Daughter, your faith has made you whole; go in peace." It was her faith and not her touch that made her whole. And this case is a good illustration of many apparently miraculous cures which attended upon Jesus' earth career, BUT WHICH HE IN NO SENSE CONSCIOUSLY WILLED. }
