\par\pard\plain \sa160\sl259\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs22\b0\i0\cb5\highlight5 15.  Each day should be devoted to miracles. The purpose of time is to enable man to learn to use it constructively. Time is thus a teaching device and a means to an end. It will cease when it is no longer useful in facilitating learning.}
\par\plain \f0\fs22\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 Time is a teaching device and a means to create God the Supreme.  God the Supreme is the God of time and space. He is evolving but it is important to remember there will come a time when God the Supreme will be complete. There will be no need for time since all potentials will be exhausted in time. The seven super universes will be settled in light and life and The Almighty Supreme will flash into existence all at once. At that moment we will all simultaneously discover God the Almighty Supreme. This is also the concept spoken of in JCIM when referring to the Sonship. To understand the course\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s perspective on Sonship and time it is important to understand the Urantia books concept of God the Supreme and our part in it. They both say the same thing. How amazing is that? UB  117:2.6 \u8220\'93There will come an end sometime to the growth of the Supreme; his status will achieve completion (in the energy-spirit sense). This termination of the evolution of the Supreme will also witness the ending of creature evolution as a part of Supremacy.\u8221\'94}
\par\pard\plain \ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 UB 117:2.2 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We have long held, however, that the present growth which characterizes creature existence in the present universe age is a function of the Supreme. We equally hold that this kind of growth is peculiar to the age of the growth of the Supreme, and that it will terminate with the completion of the growth of the Supreme.\u8221\'94}
