\par\plain \f0\fs22\b0\i0
\par\pard\plain \ql\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs24\b0\i0 Forgiveness is an absolute central theme throughout the course. It is the central theme to removing the blocks to love. With the UB we have the master plan of creation. The purpose of all this temporal existence is the creation of God the supreme. (and making the sonship whole in CIM). We will one day all join and discover God the Supreme (sonship) at the same moment. Each one of us is an irreplaceable part of the sonship. How does this play a role in our forgiveness. The course says simply see each of us as either full of love or lacking in love. If we see a lack, the natural response will be to fill that lack. No need to judge anyone as guilty, but instead lacking. If we are able to fill a lack in someone else we experience the fullness of love in ourselves. That I would call a miracle. This makes the idea of service appealing because it opens up channels to the higher mind (Holy Spirit) we cannot access any other way. }{\f6\fs24\b0\i0 So knowledge of the master plan is a motivation to see our brothers in a different light, an irreplaceable part of what we are here to accomplish.\~}
\par\pard\plain \sa160\sl259\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch \f0\fs22\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 CIM. 42 Where could your peace arise but from forgiveness? The Christ in you looks only on the truth and sees no condemnation that could need forgiveness. He is at peace because He sees no sin.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 CIM. Guilt is the only need the ego has, and as long as you identify with it, guilt will remain attractive to you.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 Urantia: 146:2.4 Even the forgiveness of sin operates in this same unerring fashion. THE FATHER IN HEAVEN HAS FORGIVEN YOU EVEN BEFORE YOU HAVE THOUGHT TO ASK HIM, but such forgiveness is not available in your personal religious experience until such a time as you forgive your fellow men. God's forgiveness in fact is not conditioned upon your forgiving your fellows, but in experience it is exactly so conditioned.}
\par\plain \f0\fs22\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0\cb5\highlight5 22. Miracles are associated with fear only because of the fallacious belief that darkness can hide. Man believes that what he cannot see does not exist, and his physical eyes cannot see in the dark. This is a very primitive solution and has led to a denial of the Spiritual eye. [1] The escape from darkness involves two stages:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0\cb5\highlight5 A. 23 The recognition that darkness cannot hide. This step usually entails fear.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0\cb5\highlight5 B. 24 The recognition that there is nothing you want to hide, even if you could. This step brings escape from fear.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 At first glance this principal seems so abstract. How is fear linked to this idea that darkness can hide us. I remember reading in the Course that there are no private thoughts. When I read it I didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t like that idea, this is the source of fear. Here is the Course quote from the text.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 CIM. Today we are again emphasizing the fact that minds are joined. This is rarely a wholly welcome idea at first, since it seems to carry with it an enormous sense of responsibility and may even be regarded as an "invasion of privacy." Yet it is a fact that there are no private thoughts. Despite your initial resistance to this idea, you will yet understand that it must be true if salvation is possible at all. And salvation must be possible because it is the Will of God.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 But it is true, Minds are linked, and the UB also says this. When our mind rises up above the seven adjutant mind spirits and connects to the Holy Spirit (spiritual eye) we all share that mind. The UB also says we have no private thoughts and there are special beings who know our every thought. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 Urantia: 28:6.19 The real nature of any service, be it rendered by man or angel, is fully revealed in the faces of these secoraphic service indicators, the Sanctities of Service. The full analysis of the true and of the hidden motives is clearly shown. These angels are indeed the mind readers, heart searchers, and soul revealers of the universe. Mortals may employ words to conceal their thoughts, but these high seconaphim lay bare the deep motives of the human heart and of the angelic mind.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 Our angels and Thought Adjusters are also keenly award of our thoughts. So this principal is in complete agreement with the UB. For those who welcome this seeming intrusion into our personal lives, fear should be lessened. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0\cb5\highlight5 23. Miracles rearrange perception and place the levels of perception in true perspective. This heals at all levels because sickness comes from confusing the levels.}
\par\plain \f0\fs22\b0\i0\cb5\highlight5
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0\cb5\highlight5  When you have become willing to hide nothing, you will not only be willing to enter into communion but will also understand peace and joy. Your commitment is not yet total, and that is why you still have more to learn than to teach. When your equilibrium stabilizes, you will be able to teach as much as you learn, which will give you the proper balance. Meanwhile, remember that no effort is wasted, for unless you remember this, you cannot avail yourselves of my efforts, which are limitless. Only eternity is real. Why not use the illusion of time constructively?}
\par\plain \f0\fs22\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93}{\f0\fs22\b0\i0\cb5\highlight5 23. Miracles rearrange perception and place the levels of perception in true perspective.}{\f0\fs22\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94 I cannot comment on the mechanisms that are at work here to correct these levels of perception but we do know levels exist from reading the UB. Beginning at the non teachable levels of mechanical mind to the seven adjutants up through the Holy Spirit, the spirit of truth to the cosmic mind. What I am learning through this study is that forgiveness is essential to open our minds to these higher levels of superconscious. And through Jesus life we see that when we reach these levels of awareness miracles do naturally happen. }
\par\plain \f0\fs22\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93}{\f0\fs22\b0\i0\cb5\highlight5 Only eternity is real. Why not use the illusion of time constructively}{\f0\fs22\b0\i0 ?\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 Some Urantia book readers have a problem with the course because it makes statements like \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Only eternity is real. Why not use the illusion of time constructively\u8221\'94 Yet we can find many references to the eternal perspective in the UB that says they consider the material world almost entirely unreal. The opposing views of time and eternity make the transition from one to the other confusing to say the least. The Course is an attempt to help us make that transition. Since time has an expiration date at least in the sense that we will exhaust all possibilities of time with the creation of the supreme, what language would you use if you were in eternity and looking on time from that perspective? Is it logical for eternal beings to reference time as an illusion? They certainly do in the UB with statements like this. \u8220\'93To material beings the spirit world is more or less unreal; to spirit beings the material world is almost entirely unreal, being merely a shadow of the substance of spirit realities.\u8221\'94 This miracle principal fits with this quote from the UB in relation to time. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 5 - (130:7.8) The time-space concept of a mind of material origin is destined to undergo successive enlargements as the conscious and conceiving personality ascends the levels of the universes. When man attains the mind intervening between the material and the spiritual planes of existence, his ideas of time-space will be enormously expanded both as to quality of perception and quantity of experience. ..\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8230\'85\u8230\'85.. And as personality passes on, upward and inward, to the transcendental levels of Deity-likeness, the time-space concept will increasingly approximate the TIMELESS AND SPACELESS concepts of the Absolutes.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0\cb5\highlight5 CIM: 24. Miracles enable man to heal the sick and raise the dead because he made sickness and death himself and can abolish both. You are a miracle, capable of creating in the likeness of your Creator. Everything else is only your own nightmare and does not exist. Only the creations of light are real.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 Me: This certainly seems at odds with the UB, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93he made sickness and death himself and can abolish it\u8221\'94. I wasn\u8217\'92t even born when Lucifer rebelled. I always wondered why our planet was put in isolation for Lucifer\u8217\'92s rebellion and Adam and Eves default. It seems unfair to make the inhabitants of a planet pay for the errors of others. But how does this look from the eternal perspective? The Course emphasizes our oneness with the Sonship as a major change in viewpoint from our individualized ego perspective. We are linked together in ways we cannot totally understand. The UB provides incredible details about our interconnectedness. But do we truly get it? The CIM puts the responsibility on us collectively for getting into this mess and places the power to correct it squarely within our collective minds. We do have the power to transcend the current misery and rise above it. The only answer to this seeming conflict between the UB and CIM is that we are all one in the grand scheme. We are all part of the Supreme Being. We are downstream from the Lucifer rebellion and the Adamic default but we are still being held accountable in some way that only makes sense from the eternal perspective. It can certainly be said that Lucifer created sickness and death. Here is similar language in the UB. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 UB 53:3.7. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93And it was with such a Declaration of Liberty that Lucifer launched his orgy of darkness and death\u8221\'94.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 Me: I suggest that what this principal is saying is that we collectively as the sonship create sickness and death and we can correct it. This may be the perspective from eternity. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0\cb5\highlight5 CIM: You are a miracle, capable of creating in the likeness of your Creator.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 Me: the UB quote below say pretty much the same thing. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 UB: 4 - (117:3.5) Mortal man is more than figuratively made in the image of God. From a physical standpoint this statement is hardly true, but with reference to certain universe potentialities it is an actual fact. In the human race, something of the same drama of evolutionary attainment is being unfolded as takes place, on a vastly larger scale, in the universe of universes. MAN, A VOLITIONAL PERSONALITY, BECOMES CREATIVE IN LIAISON WITH AN ADJUSTER, an impersonal entity, in the presence of the finite potentialities of the Supreme, and the result is the flowering of an immortal soul. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0\cb5\highlight5 CIM: Everything else is only your own nightmare and does not exist. Only the creations of light are real.}
\par\pard\plain \ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 Me: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Only the creations of light are real\u8221\'94 the UB says most of what we believe is scaffolding. What is real will be preserved within our soul.  }
\par\plain \f0\fs22\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 UB: 6 - (115:1.2) Conceptual frames of the universe are only relatively true; they are serviceable scaffolding which must eventually give way before the expansions of enlarging cosmic comprehension.}
